{"tid":2478643,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"酒吧等業界續絕食 建制派到場聲援 警方以限聚令清場","createTime":"2021-04-07T08:20:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T09:16:45.000Z","uid":362199,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b3e66ab1b8b07ac8d6e93b6b8db6bda34dda2412","tid":2478643,"uid":362199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:20:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2759979/酒吧等業界續絕食+建制派到場聲援\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2759979%2F%E9%85%92%E5%90%A7%E7%AD%89%E6%A5%AD%E7%95%8C%E7%BA%8C%E7%B5%95%E9%A3%9F%2B%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E6%B4%BE%E5%88%B0%E5%A0%B4%E8%81%B2%E6%8F%B4&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtOr6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=d10bf4b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2759979/酒吧等業界續絕食+建制派到場聲援</a><br />\n<br />\n持牌酒吧會所聯會、麻雀館、卡拉OK及會所的代表，連續第二日在政府總部外絕食，首批酒吧業代表已絕食25小時，卡拉OK業界代表將接力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n數名建制派議員到場聲援，包括經民聯張華峰、新民黨容海恩、工聯會郭偉強及民建聯陳恒鑌。容海恩表示，政府應交代需要持續「清零」多久，才會讓業界復業。郭偉強指出，擔心業界「未病死先餓死」。<br />\n<br />\n約30名業界代表到場請願，警員以限聚令為由要求他們離開，只容許絕食人士繼續在場。持牌酒吧會所聯會會長梁立仁稱，他們只是請願不是示威，會以合法方式表達訴求。"},{"pid":"9271665194ee5a3aa4e8bee58d6ebc75dfd5a123","tid":2478643,"uid":67468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:22:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76309adcfcfe87c2452cd972e9083442e640c3f9","tid":2478643,"uid":225347,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:29:07.000Z","msg":"操大陸語嘅官員&gt;局長&gt;黑警&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;獻世派廢物嘅忠誠"},{"pid":"d48df6bec879088d2c0f52640e9af250b3fa719a","tid":2478643,"uid":59037,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:30:35.000Z","msg":"支持狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df720ef076d56f9062dd8edaba3e6d3d5e4055eb","tid":2478643,"uid":131423,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":